          <td width="87%" valign="top"><h1 class="Heading">the Creative Sign Company</h1>
            <p class="text">The Creative Sign &amp; Display Company has been in the <strong>electrical sign</strong> and advertising business since 1974. We <a href="sign_repair.php">service</a> the greater Los Angeles and Southern California areas. As a family owned and operated business, we take pride in the products and services we provide. Whether you need a single <a href="channel_letters.php"><strong>channel letter sign</strong></a> or a complete <a href="sign_programs.php">sign program for your shopping center</a>, our team will from concept to completion, <a href="logo_design.php">design</a>, fabricate, and install your new sign displays.</p>
            <p class="text">We give the best warranty in the business. 5 year warranty for <a href="led_conversions.php">LED</a> and 3 year warranty for <a href="channel_letters.php">neon</a> and fluorescent. Other sign companies will only give 90 days. How is that for quality? </p>
            <p class="text">We specialize in <a href="interior_signs.php"><strong>interior signs</strong></a>, <strong><a href="monument_signs.php">outdoor signs</a></strong>, and <a href="led_conversions.php">LED lighting</a>. Be sure to visit our <a href="led_conversions.php"><strong>LED Conversions</strong></a> page to learn more about the benefits of <a href="go_green.php">going green</a>.</p>
            <p class="text">Fast <a href="sign_repair.php"><strong>sign repair</strong> service</a> for Los Angeles and Southern California areas. <a href="sign_repair.php">Sign Maintenance</a> accounts are available for all of the signs we fabricate. </p>
            <p class="text"><a href="http://www.cre8signs.com">The Creative Sign &amp; Display Company</a> is fully <a href="electrical.php">licensed</a>, bonded and insured.</p>
